# pydecklib

A deck of cards

## Installation

```bash
$ pip install pydecklib
```

## Usage

`pydecklib` can be used to use a deck of cards in a game context.

```python
from pydecklib.deck import Deck

deck = Deck()
deck.shuffle()
card = deck.draw()
```

